be asked to share your real-time geographic location information with us so we can customize your experience.&nbsp; If you agree to such additional collection, you will be able to turn off such additional collection at any time by accessing the privacy settings of your mobile device and/or through the setting in the applicable mobile application.&nbsp; Please note that by disabling or blocking any or all cookies, some features of the Product may not operate as intended, or you may not have access to features or personalization available through the Product.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>Third Party Advertisements</u>. We may use third-party advertising service vendors to serve advertisements on the Crain&rsquo;s Products. These vendors may use cookies, web beacons or similar technologies to serve you advertisements tailored to interests you have shown by browsing on this and other sites you have visited. In doing so, these vendors may collect non-personal data such as your browser type, your operating system, web pages visited, time of visits, content viewed, ads viewed, and other clickstream data. The use of cookies, web beacons or similar technologies by these advertising service vendors is subject to their own privacy policies, not ours, and we disclaim all liability in connection therewith. To learn more about third party online advertising and to opt out of this type of advertising, visit home.Autoweek.com or the Network Advertising Initiative Web site or <a href="http://www.aboutads.info">www.aboutads.info</a>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><u>Other Disclosures of Your Information</u>. We may disclose personal information if we are required to do so by law or we in good faith believe that such action is necessary to (1) comply with the law or with legal process; (2) protect and defend our rights and property; (3) protect against misuse or unauthorized use of Crain&rsquo;s Products; or (4) protect the personal safety or property of our users or the public (among other things, thi